data.text:
Taylor County Map

The County of Taylor is located in the State of Florida. Find directions to Taylor County, browse local businesses, landmarks, get current traffic estimates, road conditions, and more. According to the 2020 US Census the Taylor County population is estimated at 21,600 people. The Taylor County time zone is Eastern Daylight Time which is 5 hours behind Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).

Nearby counties include Dixie County, Jefferson County, Lafayette County, Madison County.
